<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_319_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / Wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Perlaching<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>aufgenome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>fruntlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_319_r1l3">tage cʒü ſüchen cʒü Onelſpach auf den dinſtag nach <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>frawe<ex>n</ex></expan> tag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_319_line_1576493927166_9610"><expan>Aſſu<ex>m</ex>pc<ex>ionis</ex></expan> nu ſchirſt cʒü <expan>recht<ex>er</ex></expan> tagcʒeit da cʒeſein / . vnd <expan>bıt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> erſame </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_319_r1l7"><expan>frewntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_319_r1l6">mit <expan>ga<ex>n</ex>cʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiʒʒe </ab></add> daʒ Jr vns <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>gemein<ex>er</ex></expan> Stete <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> / cʒwen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_319_r1l8">Rete leıhen vnd ſchıcken vvöllet / daʒ die beÿ den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> doſelbſt cʒü </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_319_r1l9">Onelſpach ſein auf den Montag cʒenacht 
<add><ab facs="#facs_319_line_1576493940090_9623">ſant Egıdıen abend </ab></add> als <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> tag des morgens </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_319_r1l10">ſein ſol / . vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> auf <expan>de<ex>m</ex>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag beygeſtendig / fürderlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_319_r1l11"><expan>gerat<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd beholffen ſein / . vnd getrawen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> fruntſchaft <expan>ſünderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_319_r1l12">wol / daʒ Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_319_line_1576494003936_9696">das <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>ch</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_319_line_1576494008346_9701">wıllen tün vnd </ab></add> vns des nicht vercʒeıhen wöllet / . Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_319_r1l16">in <expan>ſölıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc . </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_319_r1l18"><expan>Nördling<ex>en</ex></expan> / Dinkelſpühel / Halle / <expan>Heylſprun<ex>n</ex>e</expan> / . <expan>weiſſemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_319_r1l19">daʒ Jr vns cʒwen <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> einen ewrs Rats leıhen / . etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_319_r1l20"><expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> <expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan> vnd <expan>wınſh<ex>eim</ex></expan> <expan>ſı<ex>m</ex>pl<ex>icite</ex>r</expan> cʒwen ewrs Rats leıhen etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_319" id="159r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Ulme </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit
                                <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Perlaching<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>aufgenome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>fruntlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tage czü süchen czü Onelspach <app><note><q type="date">auf den
                        dinstag nach <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>frawe<ex>n</ex></expan> tag
                            <expan>assu<ex>m</ex>pc<ex>ionis</ex></expan> nu schirst</q>18.08.1411</note></app>, czü
                                <expan>recht<ex>er</ex></expan> tagczeit da cze sein, und
                                <expan>bit<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> ersame <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<add>mit <expan>ga<ex>n</ex>cze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleizze</add>, daz ir uns
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> und <expan>gemein<ex>er</ex></expan> stete
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> czwen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        rete leihen und schicken wöllet, daz die bey den
                        <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> doselbst czü Onelspach sein <app><note><q type="date">auf den
                            montag cze nacht <add>sant Egidien abend</add></q>31.08.1411</note></app>, als
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <app><note><q type="date">tag des morgens</q>01.09.1411</note></app> sein sol, und den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> auf
                            <expan>de<ex>m</ex>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag beygestendig fürderlich
                                <expan>gerat<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und beholffen sein. Und getrawen
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> fruntschaft
                            <expan>sünderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> wol, daz ir <add>das
                                    <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>ch</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen tün und</add> uns des nicht
                        verczeihen wöllet. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir in
                                <expan>sölich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>Nördling<ex>en</ex></expan>, Dinkelspühel, Halle,
                                <expan>Heylsprun<ex>n</ex>e</expan>,
                            <expan>Weissemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, daz ir uns czwen
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> einen ewrs rats leihen etc.
                                <expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan> und <expan>Winsh<ex>eim</ex></expan>
<expan>si<ex>m</ex>pl<ex>icite</ex>r</expan> czwen ewrs rats leihen
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
